{
  "stem": "935.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I mean, also, they all always looked like they were just poured into their uniform.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, like a window display.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he was very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he also said, to the left and to the right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But yet, he did with, the blink of an eye, whom he didn't like-- even though they walked, they were standing where the ones who were supposed to walk.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He said, you know, like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "To the truck.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there was a friend I had then-- opera singer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Wonderful opera singer-- had little kitten.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And a mother she adored, and the mother adored her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And this mother and the kitten went on the train-- went on the truck, because the mother was tired.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They were not in our wagon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And Fritzi was with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then we started marching.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the-- an SS guard, a female guard, and two male guards who walked with us, looked as bad as we do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "One was full of-- I don't know, like infectious blood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Like thousands of mosquito bites in her head.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And the uniform was lousy, and dragging their feet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I remember that, in the car, when I was in the wagon, in the cattle car-- when I was stepping outside, I stepped back once because I had my coat in there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I went back to get my coat-- my jewelry-filled coat, which I had brought all the way from Amsterdam to Belgium to Berlin, everywhere, in the cattle car, all the way to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Didn't know it was Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And then we marched and we marched and we marched, and then I saw this big sign.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Arbeit Macht Frei-- work makes free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And the interesting thing, the first thing I saw was, there was Entrance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I never saw a sign which said Exit.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
